g?size=500x500"></p><p class="img-title">晓凡“撞脸”于莎莎</p><p>近几年，晓凡主演了多部影视作品，与杨洋、陈翔、<a href="http://m.so.com/s?q=%E7%99%BD%E6%95%AC%E4%BA%AD&amp;src=newstranscode" class="qkw">白敬亭</a>合作主演了青春励志剧<a href="http://m.so.com/s?q=%E3%80%8A%E6%97%8B%E9%A3%8E%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3%E3%80%8B&amp;src=newstranscode" class="qkw">《旋风少女》</a>，在剧中饰演松柏道馆可爱的小师妹宋萍萍，这是她的首部电视剧作品。同年，她还与同门师姐江一燕、刘青云等前辈们合作主演犯罪悬疑电影<a href="http://m.so.com/s?q=%E3%80%8A%E6%B6%88%E5%A4%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%87%B6%E6%89%8B%E3%80%8B&amp;src=newstranscode" class="qkw">《消失的凶手》</a>，在片中饰演积极反对资本家剥削的学生领袖晓凡。正是晓凡真实自然不做作，活泼可爱邻家女孩的形象让她被更多人认可，人气直线飙升。</p><p><img src="http://p32.qhimg.com/t0158650e6bc1e3c321.jpg?size=500x667"></p><p>晓凡</p></div>  <footer>  <p class=tip_quick>文章内容由搜索引擎自动发现并显示为快照，不代表360新闻的立场和观点，<a target=_blank class=viewsource href="http://yule.sohu.com/20160321/n441324122.shtml">查看原文</a></p>      </footer> </article> <section class=sohu_cy> <div id=SOHUCS sid='edf06b8c24af1b9981826733eb0b2f81'></div><script id=changyan_mobile_js charset="utf-8" src="http://changyan.sohu.com/upload/mobile/wap-js/changyan_mobile.js?client_id=cyrTywwWs&conf=prod_c56aa5a54e89138d855c5ca9b31470a0" ></script> </section>  <aside id="next-news"> <h3><em>于莎莎</em>的其它新闻:</h3> <ul>    <li> <a href="/transcode?q=%E4%BA%8E%E8%8E%8E%E8%8E%8E&amp;pn=1&amp;pos=7&amp;m=6eaf3109646b01aea20a374d162069e89b7d49f9&amp;u=http%3A%2F%2Fyule.qlwb.com.cn%2F2016%2F0320%2F576564_11.shtml" data-pos="1"> 刘诗诗伴娘<b>于莎莎</b>个人资料生活照私照美照曝光 《女医明妃传》饰演紫苏获封表... </a>   <li> <a href="/transcode?q=%E4%BA%8E%E8%8E%8E%E8%8E%8E&amp;pn=1&amp;pos=8&amp;m=b13eccf59515a8e4dfdac865830e24b61b9d2706&amp;u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.zj.xinhuanet.com%2Fyltd%2F2016-03%2F14%2Fc_1118322280.htm" data-pos="2"> 袁姗姗变身女汉子 与<b>于莎莎</b>霸气合照逗笑网友 </a>   <li> <a href="/transcode?q=%E4%BA%8E%E8%8E%8E%E8%8E%8E&amp;pn=1&amp;pos=9&amp;m=454fc0a941a07f6d99755da870608431234b6842&amp;u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.zj.xinhuanet.com%2Fyltd%2F2016-03%2F14%2Fc_1118323505.htm" data-pos="3"> 对口型大作战大东COS霸王"痴情"<b>于莎莎</b> </a>  </ul> </aside>  <div c